author: National Geographic
description:
Go behind the scenes with David Blaine as he unravels his most dangerous stunt, 30 years in the making. Blaine reveals the meticulous process and the inspiration to his relentless pursuit of answering one terrifying question: How long can a man endure being in flames? Uncover the secrets of this jaw-dropping feat from Do Not Attempt.
